data.subject: Oh Holy Night
data.lyric:
Oh holy night
 The stars are brightly shining
 It is the night of the dear Savior's birth
 Long lay

data.subject: Noche De Paz
data.lyric:
Noche de paz, noche de amor
 Todo duerme en derredor
 Entre los astros que esparcen su luz
 Bella an

data.subject: Have Yourself A Merry Little Christmas
data.lyric:
Have yourself a merry little Christmas
 Let your heart be light
 From now on
 Our troubles will be o

data.subject: Jesus
data.lyric:
Hoy yo quiero recordar
 Todo lo bueno que me das
 Para crecer y valorarme
 Para entenderte y no olvi
